{
  "stem": "7455.8",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I already made $30 a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my cousin was very good to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was my mother's cousin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was the cousin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was the wife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She had no children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Loving.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And washed my hair and nourished me, stuffed in me food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I had a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I went enrolled to night school to learn English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And at night, those times in 1946, we were not afraid to go at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She was in Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And near Prospect Avenue was a night school for refugees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I walked at night and coming home late, my heels clicking, I saw my shadow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I never thought somebody's going to grab me, somebody's going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I learned English from its foundation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And when I learned English, I felt I could look for better jobs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so-- and my cousin-- my brother would come every-- for Sabbath every Friday night, stay over the weekend.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He found a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he had a furnished room, supported himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My relatives bought me dresses and suits and shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they were very good to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but I was gregarious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just wanted to tell them everything that happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes I felt, they think I talk too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But isn't it my duty to tell what was done to my family?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No matter how you could be sympathetic, nobody, nobody in this world could grasp the magnitude of this tragedy, what took place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- after awhile, they don't want to expose upon themself that pain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't want to hear it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like there are some survivors who for years did not tell, because it was too painful for them to talk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I personally felt-- my father gave us the document.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
